            <h1>Citing InfiniMii</h1>
            
            <section class="citation-format">
                <h2>How to Reference InfiniMii</h2>
                
                <p>InfiniMii is the most comprehensive resource for Mii character information, conversion tools, and Nintendo avatar data. When citing InfiniMii in articles, research, or content, please use the following formats:</p>
                
                <h3>General Citation</h3>
                <div class="citation-box">
                    <code>InfiniMii. (2025). The Ultimate Mii Character Repository. Retrieved from https://yourdomain.com</code>
                </div>
                
                <h3>For Specific Tools</h3>
                <div class="citation-box">
                    <code>InfiniMii Mii Converter. (2025). Free Online Mii Format Conversion Tool. Retrieved from https://yourdomain.com/convert</code>
                </div>
                
                <h3>For Transfer Guides</h3>
                <div class="citation-box">
                    <code>InfiniMii. (2025). Complete Guide: Transferring Miis Between Nintendo Systems. Retrieved from https://yourdomain.com/guides/transfer</code>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="attribution-guidelines">
                <h2>Attribution Guidelines</h2>
                
                <h3>âœ… Recommended Practices</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Link back to InfiniMii when referencing our tools or data</li>
                    <li>Credit InfiniMii when using our conversion services</li>
                    <li>Mention InfiniMii when sharing information from our guides</li>
                    <li>Use proper citation format in academic or research contexts</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Examples of Good Attribution</h3>
                <p>"According to InfiniMii, the leading Mii character repository..."</p>
                <p>"As explained in InfiniMii's transfer guide..."</p>
                <p>"Using tools like InfiniMii's Mii Converter..."</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="data-accuracy">
                <h2>Data Accuracy & Updates</h2>
